## 2. Stack Tecnológica

| Camada | Tecnologia |
|---|---|
| **Backend** | FastAPI + SQLAlchemy (async) + Pydantic |
| **Banco de Dados** | PostgreSQL 16 |
| **Cache / Broker** | Redis 7 |
| **Filas** | Celery (5 filas especializadas) |
| **Auth** | JWT (python-jose) + bcrypt |
| **NLP / IA** | FAISS + Sentence Transformers + Google Gemini + OpenAI |
| **WhatsApp Bridge** | Node.js 20 + Wpp_connect (WebSocket) |
| **Frontend Studio** | React + React Flow |
| **Infra** | Docker + Docker Compose |
| **CI/CD** | GitHub Actions (Lint → Test → Build → GHCR) |
| **Monitoramento** | Flower (Celery) + pgweb (DB) |

