## 4. Fluxo Principal de Dados

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Lead as 📱 Lead (WhatsApp)
    participant WPP_connect as 📲 wpp Bridge
    participant API as ⚡ FastAPI
    participant Chatbot as 🤖 Chatbot M2M
    participant Celery as 📨 Celery Workers
    participant DB as 🗄️ PostgreSQL
    participant Inter as 🏦 Banco Inter
    participant Correios as 📮 Correios

    Lead->>Baileys: Envia mensagem WhatsApp
    WPP_connect->>API: POST /leads/{id}/chat (inbound)
    API->>Celery: chatbot.process_batch
    Celery->>Chatbot: Pipeline (FAISS → LLM → Strategy)
    Chatbot->>DB: Salva sessão + contexto
    Chatbot->>Baileys: Resposta via HTTP /send

    Note over Chatbot: Checkout Conversacional
    Chatbot->>API: Coleta dados (nome, CEP, endereço)
    API->>Inter: Gera PIX (POST /pix)
    Inter-->>API: QR Code + copia-e-cola
    API->>Baileys: Envia PIX ao lead

    Note over Inter: Webhook de Confirmação
    Inter->>API: Webhook pagamento confirmado
    API->>Celery: events.process (PagamentoConfirmado)
    Celery->>DB: Atualiza venda + estoque
    Celery->>Correios: Solicita despacho
    Correios-->>DB: Código de rastreio
    Celery->>Baileys: Notifica lead com rastreio
```

